---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Music/Production Sessions — Threads" description="Session log and release prep notes." theme="threads">
  <article class="thread-doc">
    <a href="/threads" class="thread-back">← Back to threads</a>
    <h1>Music / Production Sessions</h1>
    <p class="thread-lede">Session-by-session notes for arrangement, sound design, and release sequencing.</p>

    <h2>Session workflow</h2>
    <p>Each session closes with one bounce, one note about what failed, and one next-step prompt for the following session.</p>

    <h2>Release readiness</h2>
    <p>Tracks move to release once arrangement, loudness targets, and visual packaging are all documented in one place.</p>

    <h2>Related pages</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/link-hub">Link hub</a></li>
      <li><a href="/social/spotify">Spotify social page</a></li>
      <li><a href="/social/untitled">Untitled social page</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .thread-doc { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 auto; }
  .thread-back { color: var(--tone-accent-glow); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--tone-accent) 32%, transparent); }
  .thread-doc h1 { margin: 0.75rem 0 0.7rem; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.7rem); line-height: 1.1; }
  .thread-lede { margin: 0; font-size: 1.08rem; color: var(--tone-muted); }
  .thread-doc h2 { margin-top: 1.3rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .thread-doc p { line-height: 1.7; }
</style>
